01:46:29,940 --> 01:46:31,940
 Ja.

861
01:46:31,940 --> 01:46:35,940
 Ajde ovako da te pitam.

862
01:46:35,940 --> 01:46:37,940
 Lud.

863
01:46:37,940 --> 01:46:41,940
 Znači, life of our dreams.

864
01:46:41,940 --> 01:46:47,940
 Kako ti vidiš život iz svojih snova?

